  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3471340/extras/82a82488ddcc0380f47ab220e744a489.avif?t=1741991416\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3471340/extras_big/82a82488ddcc0380f47ab220e744a489.avif?t=1741991416 width=800 height=1992 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Storied Sword is An 8-bit action-adventure where you play as Cedric and Orchid, desperately trying to retrieve the fabled Storied Sword from the evil clutches of the dark sorcerer Vectre!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels include: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Interesting Enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Weapon Pick Ups</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fast Methodical Combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Environmental Hazards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Difficult Boss Fights</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Birds.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3471340/extras/82a82488ddcc0380f47ab220e744a489.avif?t=1741991416\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3471340/extras_big/82a82488ddcc0380f47ab220e744a489.avif?t=1741991416 width=800 height=1992 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Storied Sword is An 8-bit action-adventure where you play as Cedric and Orchid, desperately trying to retrieve the fabled Storied Sword from the evil clutches of the dark sorcerer Vectre!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels include: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Interesting Enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Weapon Pick Ups</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fast Methodical Combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Environmental Hazards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Difficult Boss Fights</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Birds.</p>",
